{"name":"Lotus Leaf Kata","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-teal-blue.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 2 Martial Advance &bull; Lotus Art</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites&nbsp;</strong><em>Lotus Art: Sage's Stance</em>, Martial 5, Dodge 5</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>While in&nbsp;<em>Sage's Stance</em>, you gain a +3 bonus to Parry checks.</p>","xpCost":300,"hpBonus":2,"fpBonus":1},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DMJ2eW9M3ZM27Qdu"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768054882870,"modifiedTime":1774471761036,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"ulUPWsR8BIXGCVfT"}
{"name":"Weapon Focus","type":"advance","img":"icons/skills/melee/maneuver-sword-katana-yellow.webp","system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Martial Advance, Tier 2 &bull; Weapon</strong></p>\n<p>Prerequisites: None<br>Effect: You may pick a class of melee weapon (such as sword, hammer, ...); all attack rolls with a weapon of the specified type gain a +2 bonus. You may take this advance multiple times, but each one must be for a different type of weapon.</p>","xpCost":300,"hpBonus":2,"fpBonus":1},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.yysfmGAsXHUaabut"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770410653083,"modifiedTime":1774471772775,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"3b9wIj4TRC2pLHHi"}
{"name":"Monkey Grip","type":"advance","img":"icons/skills/melee/unarmed-punch-fist.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.8m3nxrYRkl3CTAvS"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Passive, Martial, Tier 2</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-973efe10-7fff-efb8-7a79-6a3b131542f4\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Effect: You can wield a two-handed weapon in one hand. When you do so, you gain a -2 penalty to attack rolls with that weapon.</span></p>","xpCost":375,"hpBonus":4,"fpBonus":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774471786824,"modifiedTime":1774471786824,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"1oJjwIidzVWZUgrx"}
{"name":"Pursuit","type":"advance","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.6VzpcwNWKL3EZ5BD"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-7935c9dc-7fff-1e72-3e02-3332d193957c\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Passive, Martial, Rank 1</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prerequisites: Opportunity Attack</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Effect: When you use your opportunity attack reaction, after the attack resolves, you can immediately move up to your speed in the direction of the triggering enemy. You must end your move adjacent to the triggering enemy if possible.</span></p>","xpCost":250,"hpBonus":2,"fpBonus":1},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774471924558,"modifiedTime":1774471924558,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"MG7QVLYNK5242pbV"}
